  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Videolaryngoscopes become widely used. The aim of this study is to compare McGrath Mac
      videolaryngoscope to conventional MacIntosh laryngoscope in patients without known risk of
      difficult of mask ventilation and of tracheal intubation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
